tweet: Congrats to @Strom_Peterson on the passage of HB 1961, authorizing courts to waive name change fees for folks facing financial hardship. The AGO supports this move to reduce barriers for the transgender community and survivors of DV. #waleg

tweet: Congratulations to longtime labor champion @KarenKeiser1 for getting SSB 5890 across the finish line. This bill provides long-overdue worker protections on hazardous nuclear sites. The AGO is very pleased to see SSB 5890 become law. #waleg
